# OneDrive conflict copies (this repo currently lives under OneDrive, which
# creates "<name>-<DEVICE>.<ext>" duplicates of edited files). Never commit them.
# NOTE: keeping a repo's .git under OneDrive is unsafe — move it out of OneDrive.
*-MSI.*
*-MSI/
*-DESKTOP-*.*

